article.headline: Murphy's law: USC tops Eastern Illinois in Waikiki Classic
article.linkText: Murphy's law: USC tops Eastern Illinois in Waikiki Classic
article.story:
HONOLULU (AP) -- Eshaya Murphy scored 17 points to lead Southern California (No. 23 ESPN/USA Today, No. 24 AP) to a 68-53 victory over Eastern Illinois on Sunday night in the Waikiki Beach Marriott Classic.

Chloe Kerr added 15 points, Jamie Hagiya had 12 and Cailee LeNoir 10 for the Women of Troy (2-0). Ellen Canale led the Panthers (0-1) with 19 points, and Megan Sparks and Tangie Sellers each had 11.
